@startuml
' Activity Diagram - Order Tracking & Notifications (Release 1 / MVP)
skinparam swimlaneOrientation vertical

title Activity - Tracking & Notifications (UC-D6)

|System|
start
:Order status changes
(from restaurant/shipper/admin action);
:Validate transition [BR-7];
:Persist new status + history;
:Create notification event;

fork
  ' Customer delivery path
  |System|
  :Route event to Customer;
  if (Customer app state?) then (Foreground)
    :Send WebSocket update (SLA <= 5s);
    if (WebSocket connected?) then (Yes)
      |Customer|
      :Receive in-app status update;
    else (No)
      |Customer|
      :Detect disconnect;
      :Reconnect;
      |System|
      :Sync latest status on reconnect;
      |Customer|
      :Show latest status;
    endif

  else (Background/Closed)
    |External Systems (Push Provider)|
    :Deliver push notification;
    |Customer|
    :Receive push;
    :Open app later;
    |System|
    :Sync latest status on open;
    |Customer|
    :Show latest status;
  endif

  |System|
  if (Push/WebSocket degraded?) then (Yes)
    :Enable polling fallback;
    |Customer|
    :Poll latest status periodically;
    |System|
    :Return latest status;
  endif

fork again
  ' Restaurant path
  |System|
  :Route event to Restaurant;
  :Send in-app update;
  |External Systems (Push Provider)|
  :Send optional alert
  (e.g., cancellation/assignment);
  |Restaurant|
  :See updated order state;

fork again
  ' Shipper path
  |System|
  :Route event to assigned shipper;
  if (Status requires shipper action?) then (Yes)
    |External Systems (Push Provider)|
    :Send dispatch/status push;
  endif
  |Shipper|
  :See updated order state;

fork again
  ' Admin path
  |System|
  :Route event to Admin monitoring;
  :Refresh dashboard data
  (freshness <= 60s);
  |Admin|
  :View updated status;
end fork

|System|
if (Order cancelled?) then (Yes)
  :Attach cancellation reason;
  :Notify affected parties;
endif

|System|
if (Status = Picked Up?) then (Yes)
  :Provide shipper contact details
  to customer (controlled access);
endif

stop

@enduml
